TopicTitle: Whatever happened to the I dream of Space comp?

Articles.Content: So a little while ago there was a screenshot competition where the winner would win a sub orbital flight into space... what happened?
Shhhh mib will come haha but yeah good question
I think it finished. I can't think of anything else, after this massive of amount of time has gone by.
The contest was completed, the winners were announced and the whole subforum was lost in the great forum catastrophe...

So... Who won the contest?

And will there really be a sub-orbital tour?
